text: Hugo César Cisneros Rodríguez (born November 27, 1994 in Cuerámaro, Guanajuato) is a Mexican professional footballer who last played for Querétaro F.C. Premier. He made his professional debut with Cimarrones de Sonora during an Ascenso MX defeat to Mineros de Zacatecas on 22 July 2016. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Cimarrones de Sonora players Category:Ascenso MX players Category:Liga Premier de México players Category:Tercera División de México players Category:Footballers from Guanajuato
